snippet.title: A Harmonic Series Paradox (TANTON Mathematics)
snippet.description: Here's a cute, but disturbing, geometric interpretation of two famous series in mathematics: the harmonic series (which sums to an infinite value) and the Basel series (which sums to a finite value). Put the two together and ... WHOA!
